  "reason_thou": "1. Understanding the Issue:\n\nThe assertion failure in
`getLastInstructionInBundle` indicates that the SLP vectorizer is encountering
a TreeEntry bundle that violates the expected constraints. The assertion checks
that either:\n1. We have gathered loads with valid indices, OR\n2. All scalars
