uninitialized, which causes the assertion to fail because none of the expected
conditions are met.\n\n2. Analyzing `opt`'s Log:\n\nThe log shows that the SLP
vectorizer is attempting to vectorize GEP indices:\n- \"SLP: Analyzing a
